headline: ABT Stock to Gain From FDA IDE Approval for Its Coronary IVL System
summary: Abbott's Coronary IVL System wins FDA IDE nod, offering a potential new treatment for arterial calcium blockages.

headline: Abbott gets FDA nod to begin IVL trial after rivals buy up competition
summary: J&J acquired the IVL device maker Shockwave Medical last year for $13.1 billion, and Boston Scientific agreed to buy Bolt Medical in January for up to $664 million.
